Hessian Matching Units

- Tabular Experiments:
  - Baselines: main_tabular_baselines trains the MLP baselines
  - Other Architectures: main_tabular_HMU trains the HMU variants, including RBFs and also the Pi-Net variants

- Synthetic Experiments:
  - synthetic_scaling_combined runs the training on the six different types of manifold classification problems for MLPs, RBFs and HMUs of single-hidden layer.
